ESTATE OF Thalia DUKES
v.
CRAIGE 256P19-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 14, 2019

Tony C. Thomas, For Thomas, Tony C.

H. Kenneth Stephens, II, Attorney at Law, Wilmington, For Craige, Lawrence S.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th of June 2019 by Plaintiff for North Carolina Supreme Court to Assume Jurisdiction:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2019."
